    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866640/extras/7d7f6b5f3e7777bf2be79b0f876e9a30.poster.avif?t=1760809581\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866640/extras/7d7f6b5f3e7777bf2be79b0f876e9a30.webm?t=1760809581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866640/extras/7d7f6b5f3e7777bf2be79b0f876e9a30.mp4?t=1760809581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于游戏</h2>Kronos 是一款战术战斗模拟器，融合了战术、战略和激烈的第一人称战斗元素。在一个持续了几个世纪的无休止战争的世界里，这场战争的起源早已被遗忘，但主要目标仍然很明确。捍卫你的统治权，免受敌方人类指挥官及其一次性机器人军队的侵害。<br><br>剩下的唯一选择是成功或加入无数可能的宇宙统治者名单。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一次性军队</h2><br>管理个人一次性军队，夺取和控制敌对派系的领土。带领机器人仆从从前线出发，亲自发出命令，祈祷他们微小的电子大脑能够承受压力。在你的硅朋友耗尽战斗精神之前赢得胜利。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866640/extras/52c0638494658895266401b4669adc5a.poster.avif?t=1760809581\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866640/extras/52c0638494658895266401b4669adc5a.webm?t=1760809581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866640/extras/52c0638494658895266401b4669adc5a.mp4?t=1760809581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不可回收的敌人</h2><br>敌军不会无所事事地等待。您是否会采取龟缩防守并冒着失去势头的风险？还是以微弱优势取胜，占领足够的土地以保持压力？用炮塔加固每个领土并升级领先机器人以组建一支小型精锐军队？或许尝试使用廉价的消耗性机器人进行大规模攻击？数量有其自身的质量。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866640/extras/9d793328925102cea793dd98b17cf69f.poster.avif?t=1760809581\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866640/extras/9d793328925102cea793dd98b17cf69f.webm?t=1760809581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866640/extras/9d793328925102cea793dd98b17cf69f.mp4?t=1760809581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >要掌握的技能</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866640/extras/551c40433a71b77ddf66c2f19635b125.poster.avif?t=1760809581\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866640/extras/551c40433a71b77ddf66c2f19635b125.webm?t=1760809581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866640/extras/551c40433a71b77ddf66c2f19635b125.mp4?t=1760809581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>没有起始构建或优势 - 战场决定谁留下。掌握 5 种主要武器、防御阵地和机器人构建。挑战朋友进行一轮有益健康的机器人屠杀！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866640/extras/bd20e89eade45b653afcb99cb6c6bdcc.poster.avif?t=1760809581\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866640/extras/bd20e89eade45b653afcb99cb6c6bdcc.webm?t=1760809581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866640/extras/bd20e89eade45b653afcb99cb6c6bdcc.mp4?t=1760809581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
